  {
    "id": "microhistories § the-stories-behind-the-milestones § p1",
    "section": "the-stories-behind-the-milestones",
    "tag": "p",
    "en": "Out of This World 25 uses <strong class=\"x-el x-el-span c1-22 c1-23 c1-b c1-dl c1-3m c1-51 c1-dm\">Microhistories</strong> to explore the people, moments, technologies, and ideas that shaped Canada’s journey in space.",
