    "status": "pending"
  },
  {
    "id": "microhistories § the-stories-behind-the-milestones § p2",
    "section": "the-stories-behind-the-milestones",
    "tag": "p",
    "en": "These stories go beyond the headlines. They help reveal how major achievements — from <strong class=\"x-el x-el-span c1-22 c1-23 c1-b c1-dl c1-3m c1-51 c1-dm\">Chris Hadfield’s 2001 mission</strong> to <strong class=\"x-el x-el-span c1-22 c1-23 c1-b c1-dl c1-3m c1-51 c1-dm\">Jeremy Hansen’s Artemis II journey around the Moon</strong>  — are shaped through collaboration, innovation, preparation, and imagination.",
    "fr": "",
    "status": "pending"
  },
  {
    "id": "microhistories § the-stories-behind-the-milestones § p3",
    "section": "the-stories-behind-the-milestones",
    "tag": "p",
    "en": "As OOTW25 grows, Microhistories will become part of the project’s original storytelling core, helping students, families, educators, and partners engage more deeply with Canada’s past and future in space.",
